quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,111,"(Kumbuchilani) lyuŵa lyataachiika mundu jwalijose ali nkuliichenjela nsyene, ni tachilipidwa mundu jwalijose mwakwanila pa yawapanganyisye, soni ŵanyao ngasaŵa ŵakutendedwa lupuso"
  16,112,"Soni Allah apeleche chilandanyo cha Musi (wa Maaka) wawaliji wantunjelele soni wakutamilichika, lyauichililaga lisiki lyakwe mwawinji kuumila malo galigose, nambo wakaaniile indimba ya Allah, basi Allah ŵaupele kupasya chiwaalo chasala ni woga ligongo lya yaŵaliji (achinsyene musio) ali nkutenda"
  16,113,"Soni chisimu chene jwaichilile Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwakuumila mu ŵanganyapeo, nambo ŵankaaniile, basi ni yakwembekenye ilagasyo kutendaga ŵanganyao ali ŵakulitenda lupuso"
  16,114,"Basi lyagani mu yampele Allah yaili ya halaal nambo soni yambone, ni ntogoleleje ukoto wa Allah nam’baga jenumanja nkun’galagatila Jwelepejo"
  16,115,"Chisimu (Allah) ayitesile haraam kukwenu (kulya) chibudu, myasi, nyama jeguluŵe ni chachikolanjilidwe (lina linepe) lyangaŵaga lya Allah pakuchisikita (kuŵa mbepesi ja akumasoka), nambo jwachasingalilwe (nikulya cha haraamucho) mwangali kuchiluumba kapena kusumba mpika, basi (ngaapata sambi) chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"
  16,116,"Ni ngasim’bechetaga yakwayana ni ayila yasikusimulila ndimi syenu mwaunami (kuti): “Ayi ya halaal, ayi ya haraam,” kuti munsepelele Allah unami. Chisimu aŵala ŵaakunsepelela Allah unami nganaŵa apundile"
  16,117,"Kusengwa kwannono (chikuŵe kwao pa duniya pano), nambo akwete kupata ŵanganyao ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope (ku Akhera)"
  16,118,"Ni ku aŵala ŵaŵaliji Ayuda twakanyisye (kulya) yatwansimbile kala, ni nganitwatenda Uwwe lupuso, nambo achimisyene ni ŵaŵaliji nkulitenda lupuso"